        <ul>
            <li>Invest in quality, reusable containers to make portioning and storage easy.</li>
            <li>Prep ingredients, like chopping vegetables or cooking grains, in advance to save time.</li>
            <li>Batch cook recipes and freeze individual portions for grab-and-go meals.</li>
